        </div>
        <div class="bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 rounded-xl p-6 border-2 border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-800">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-400">Carbohydrates</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">Primary energy source. Fuels workouts and supports athletic performance.</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-500 mt-2 font-semibold">4 calories per gram</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-amber-50 dark:bg-amber-900/20 rounded-xl p-6 border-2 border-amber-200 dark:border-amber-800">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-amber-700 dark:text-amber-400">Fat</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">Supports hormone production, nutrient absorption, and sustained energy.</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-500 mt-2 font-semibold">9 calories per gram</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- How It Works -->
    <div class="bg-emerald-50 dark:bg-emerald-900/20 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-12">
